'''Faissol Fahad Bolade Gnonlonfin''' (wavutse 1985) n'umuyobozi wa firime akaba  n'umu producer.

Mu mwaka wa 2012, Gnonlonfin yakoze ifoto ye ya mbere, ''Obalé le chasseur'', agaragaza umuturage wo muri Bénine winjiye mu itsinda ry’abahigi. Yize kuriyi ngingo imyaka ibiri kandi yitegereza impaka hagati yabahiga gakondo nabashinzwe kubungabunga inyamaswa.  Nk’uko uwahoze ari umwarimu Jean-François Hautin abitangaza ngo umuzungu ntabwo yashoboraga gufata amashusho neza umuhango w'abahiga. Filime ya kabiri ya Gnonlonfin ''Ni ici ni ailleur'' isuzuma icyerekezo cyo kurwanya ikoreshwa rya gaze ya shale muri Ardèche, ikayihuza no gukuramo umutungo muri [[Afurika]]. 

Nyuma yo kwibanda ku documentaire, inyinshi muri zo zabonye ibihembo, Gnonlonfin yatangiye gukora ibihimbano mu 2014. Muri 2017, yakoranye na Berni Goldblat hamwe na sosiyete ikora Les Lesms du Djabadjah kuri ''Wallay'' .  Yasohowe cyane, itorwa mu iserukiramuco rya Filime rya Carthage 2017.  Muri Werurwe 2018, Gnonlonfin yayoboye amahugurwa yo gutunganya amashusho muri [[Burukina Faso|Burkinafaso]]. 

Gnonlonfin yashinze isosiyete ikora Merveilles Production kugirango ishishikarize abakora firime. Yibera cyane mubufaransa ariko amara hafi amezi abiri mumwaka muri Bénin. 
